modules.description: Handles expression transformations for array JIT compilation, including list collection, dimension specification conversion, and ndarray constant construction. Works with OCaml AST expressions, long identifiers, and dimension type variants. Used to generate optimized array operations and manipulate multi-dimensional array expressions during PPX rewriting.

Handles transformation of array expressions during PPX compilation, including list flattening, dimension handling, and ndarray constant generation. Operates on OCaml AST nodes, long identifiers, and dimension type representations. Used to optimize array operations and process multi-dimensional array literals in user code.
